    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="reminders-reddit" class="premium-card p-6 border-l-4 border-[var(--c-accent)] mt-6 scroll-mt-28">
    <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-base">Reddit &amp; NeedAFriend</h3>
        <p class="text-[11px] text-[var(--c-text-dim)] leading-relaxed mt-0.5">Shared invite and post defaults for <code class="text-[10px]">/promote</code>, per-subreddit flair rows, and the <strong class="text-[var(--c-text-muted)]">NeedAFriend</strong> weekly thread fields.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-6 p-5 rounded-xl border border-[var(--c-accent-soft-ring)] bg-[var(--c-card)]/70 space-y-5">
      <p class="text-[11px] text-[var(--c-text-dim)] leading-relaxed">
        <strong class="text-[var(--c-text-muted)]">Promotion targets</strong> — one row per subreddit (same invite link for all). Enter the subreddit name, then use <strong>Find Flairs</strong> to load that subreddit’s link flairs and pick one to save. If Reddit API credentials are not configured on the host, flair loading will fail (posting from <code class="text-[10px]">/promote</code> still uses the bot’s Reddit account).
      </p>
      <textarea id="reddit_promotion_targets" class="hidden" aria-hidden="true"></textarea>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="sm:col-span-2">
          <label class="field-label">Invite link (all promotion subreddits)</label>
          <input type="url" id="reddit_promotion_link" class="field-input" placeholder="https://discord.gg/..." />
          <p class="field-hint">Discord invite URL used for every <code class="text-[10px]">/promote</code> link post.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="sm:col-span-2">
          <label class="field-label">Default post title</label>
          <input type="text" id="reddit_promotion_title" class="field-input" />
        </div>
        <div class="sm:col-span-2">
          <label class="field-label">Default post body</label>
          <textarea id="reddit_promotion_body" rows="4" class="field-input"></textarea>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="w-full text-left border-collapse min-w-[520px]">
          <thead>
            <tr class="text-[10px] uppercase font-bold text-[var(--c-text-dim)] border-b border-[var(--c-card-border)]">
              <th class="py-2.5 pr-2 w-[130px]">Subreddit</th>
              <th class="py-2.5 pr-2 min-w-[190px]">Link flair</th>
              <th class="py-2 w-10"></th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody id="redditPromotionTargetsBody" class="divide-y divide-[var(--c-card-border)]"></tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
      <button type="button" onclick="addRedditPromotionRow()" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-2 rounded-lg text-xs font-bold border border-[var(--c-input-border)] bg-[var(--c-input)] hover:bg-[var(--c-card-border)] transition-colors">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4v16m8-8H4"/></svg>
        Add subreddit
      </button>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-5 pt-2 border-t border-[var(--c-card-border)]">
      <div class="sm:col-span-2">
        <h4 class="text-sm font-bold text-[var(--c-text)] mb-2">NeedAFriend weekly thread</h4>
        <p class="text-[11px] text-[var(--c-text-dim)] mb-4">Used by <code class="text-[10px]">/needafriend</code> (separate from /promote).</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <label class="field-label">NeedAFriend Subreddit</label>
        <input type="text" id="needafriend_subreddit" class="field-input" />
      </div>
      <div>
        <label class="field-label">NeedAFriend Thread Title</label>
        <input type="text" id="needafriend_thread_title" class="field-input" />
      </div>
      <div class="sm:col-span-2">
        <label class="field-label">NeedAFriend Comment Body</label>
        <textarea id="needafriend_comment" rows="4" class="field-input"></textarea>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ SOCIAL & FUN -->
<section id="social" class="mb-10 page-section hidden">
  <div class="mb-6">
    <h2 class="section-heading mb-1">
      <svg class="w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 3v4M3 5h4M6 17v4m-2-2h4m5-16l2.286 6.857L21 12l-7.714 2.143L11 21l-2.286-6.857L1 12l7.714-2.143L11 3z" />
      </svg>
      Social & Fun
    </h2>
    <p class="text-[11px] text-[var(--c-text-dim)] leading-relaxed"><strong class="text-[var(--c-text-muted)]">Media-only</strong> channels and keyword or regex <strong class="text-[var(--c-text-muted)]">auto-reactions</strong>.</p>
  </div>

  <div id="social-restricted" class="premium-card p-6 border-l-4 border-[var(--c-accent)] scroll-mt-28">
    <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-base">Restricted Channels (Media Only)</h3>
        <p class="text-[11px] text-[var(--c-text-dim)] leading-relaxed mt-0.5">Keeps a channel to <strong class="text-[var(--c-text-muted)]">GIFs, stickers, and reactions</strong> by removing plain text posts.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[var(--c-accent)]/10 flex items-center justify-center text-[var(--c-accent)]">
        <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14.828 14.828a4 4 0 01-5.656 0M9 10h.01M15 10h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" /></svg>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-5 py-2">
      <div class="sm:col-span-2">
        <label class="field-label">Creative Channel</label>
        <select id="notext_channel" class="field-input channel-select"></select>
        <p class="field-hint">Any standard text message sent in this channel will be politely removed.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="social-auto-reactions" class="premium-card p-6 border-l-4 border-[var(--c-accent)] mt-6 scroll-mt-28">
    <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-base">Keywords &amp; Auto-Reactions</h3>
        <p class="text-[11px] text-[var(--c-text-dim)] leading-relaxed mt-0.5">Emoji reactions from <strong class="text-[var(--c-text-muted)]">whole-word keywords</strong> or optional regex rows (saved with the table below).</p>
      </div>
      <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[var(--c-accent)]/10 flex items-center justify-center text-[var(--c-accent)]">
        <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14.828 14.828a4 4 0 01-5.656 0M9 10h.01M15 10h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" /></svg>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="overflow-hidden border border-[var(--c-accent-soft-ring)] rounded-xl mt-4">
      <table class="w-full text-left border-collapse">
        <thead class="bg-[var(--c-input)] text-[var(--c-text-dim)] text-[10px] uppercase font-bold tracking-wider">
          <tr>
            <th class="px-4 py-3">Keyword / phrase</th>
            <th class="px-2 py-3 w-24 text-center" title="Enable only if you need full regular expressions">Regex</th>
            <th class="px-4 py-3">Emoji (string or ID)</th>
            <th class="px-4 py-3 text-right">Action</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody id="autoReactionTableBody" class="divide-y divide-[var(--c-card-border)]">
          <!-- Populated by JS -->
        </tbody>
      </table>
      <div class="p-4 bg-[var(--c-input)]/30 border-t border-[var(--c-card-border)] flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-3">
        <button type="button" onclick="addAutoReactionRow()" class="text-xs font-bold text-[var(--c-accent)] hover:text-[var(--c-accent-strong)] transition-colors inline-flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4v16m8-8H4"/></svg>
          Add New Pattern
        </button>
        <button type="button" onclick="saveAutoReactions()" class="btn-dash-primary p-2.5 min-h-[44px] min-w-[44px] shrink-0" aria-label="Save patterns" title="Save patterns">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 shrink-0 pointer-events-none" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 16.5v2.25A2.25 2.25 0 005.25 21h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0021 18.75V16.5M16.5 12L12 16.5m0 0L7.5 12m4.5 4.5V3"/></svg>
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-6 text-[11px] text-[var(--c-text-dim)] space-y-2 leading-relaxed">
      <p>Click the <strong class="text-[var(--c-text-muted)]">save</strong> icon when you’re finished editing.</p>
      <p><strong class="text-[var(--c-text-muted)]">Keyword mode (default):</strong> type a word or phrase — matching is <strong class="text-[var(--c-text-muted)]">case-insensitive</strong> and uses <strong class="text-[var(--c-text-muted)]">whole words</strong> (so <span class="font-mono text-[var(--c-text-muted)]">cat</span> won’t match <span class="font-mono text-[var(--c-text-muted)]">category</span>). Special regex characters are treated as plain text.</p>
      <p><strong class="text-[var(--c-text-muted)]">Regex column:</strong> turn on only for full patterns; you can still use literals like <span class="font-mono text-[var(--c-text-muted)]">/dubz/i</span>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ MAINTENANCE -->
<section id="maintenance" class="mb-10 page-section hidden">
  <div class="mb-6">
    <h2 class="section-heading mb-1">
      <svg class="w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 4v5h.582M20 20v-5h-.581M5 9a7 7 0 0114 0v6H5V9z" /></svg>
      Maintenance
    </h2>
    <p class="text-[11px] text-[var(--c-text-dim)] leading-relaxed">Inspect the bot and <strong class="text-[var(--c-text-muted)]">SQLite</strong> store, sync <strong class="text-[var(--c-text-muted)]">Discord</strong> with dashboard caches, run backfills, manage <strong class="text-[var(--c-text-muted)]">sessions</strong>, and export or restore Keyv.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
    <p id="maintenance-diagnostics" class="maint-group-label lg:col-span-2 scroll-mt-28">Diagnostics &amp; SQLite</p>

    <div class="card p-5 space-y-3 lg:col-span-2">
      <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-[var(--c-text)]">Deep Health</h3>
      <p class="text-[11px] text-[var(--c-text-dim)] leading-relaxed">Shows process details, <strong class="text-[var(--c-text-muted)]">Discord gateway</strong> latency and connection state, and an <strong class="text-[var(--c-text-muted)]">SQLite</strong> integrity check plus a quick read/write probe. <strong class="text-[var(--c-text-muted)]">Export Diagnostics</strong> saves the same snapshot for sharing with support.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        <button type="button" onclick="loadDeepHealth()" class="btn-dash-secondary btn-dash-sm">Refresh</button>
        <button type="button" onclick="exportDiagnosticsBundle()" class="btn-dash-secondary btn-dash-sm">Export Diagnostics</button>
      </div>
      <pre id="deepHealthPre" class="text-[10px] text-[var(--c-text-muted)] font-mono whitespace-pre-wrap break-words max-h-72 overflow-y-auto p-3 rounded-lg bg-[var(--c-input)] border border-[var(--c-input-border)] mt-2">Tap Refresh.</pre>
    </div>

    <div class="card p-5 space-y-3">
      <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-[var(--c-text)]">Keyv Storage Report</h3>
      <p class="text-[11px] text-[var(--c-text-dim)] leading-relaxed">Summarizes row counts and approximate payload size per namespace from the <code class="text-[10px]">keyv</code> table. The <strong class="text-[var(--c-text-muted)]">largest keys</strong> list helps you find rows that may be slowing queries or using disk.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        <button type="button" onclick="loadStorageReport()" class="btn-dash-secondary btn-dash-sm">Refresh Report</button>
      </div>
      <pre id="storageReportPre" class="text-[10px] text-[var(--c-text-muted)] font-mono whitespace-pre-wrap break-words max-h-56 overflow-y-auto p-3 rounded-lg bg-[var(--c-input)] border border-[var(--c-input-border)] mt-2">Open this section or tap Refresh Report.</pre>
    </div>

    <div class="card p-5 space-y-3">
      <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-[var(--c-text)]">SQLite Maintenance</h3>
      <p class="text-[11px] text-[var(--c-text-dim)] leading-relaxed"><strong class="text-[var(--c-text-muted)]">Analyze</strong> refreshes planner statistics for better query plans. <strong class="text-[var(--c-text-muted)]">Pragma optimize</strong> runs routine internal maintenance. <strong class="text-[var(--c-text-muted)]">Vacuum</strong> compacts the database file but needs exclusive access and often fails while the bot still has the database open.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        <button type="button" onclick="runSqliteMaint('analyze')" class="btn-dash-secondary btn-dash-sm">
          <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 shrink-0 opacity-90" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"/></svg>
          Analyze
        </button>
        <button type="button" onclick="runSqliteMaint('optimize')" class="btn-dash-secondary btn-dash-sm">
          <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 shrink-0 opacity-90" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 3v4M3 5h4M6 17v4m-2-2h4m5-16l2.286 6.857L21 12l-5.714 2.143L13 21l-2.286-6.857L5 12l5.714-2.143L13 3z"/></svg>
          Optimize
        </button>
        <button type="button" onclick="runSqliteMaint('vacuum')" class="btn-dash-secondary btn-dash-sm">
          <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 8h14M5 8a2 2 0 110-4h14a2 2 0 110 4M5 8v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V8m-9 4h4"/></svg>
          Vacuum
        </button>
      </div>
      <pre id="sqliteMaintPre" class="hidden text-[10px] text-[var(--c-text-muted)] font-mono whitespace-pre-wrap break-words max-h-32 overflow-y-auto p-3 rounded-lg bg-[var(--c-input)] border border-[var(--c-input-border)] mt-2"></pre>
    </div>

    <!-- Migration Utility -->
    <div id="migrationCard" class="card p-5 space-y-3 hidden lg:col-span-2 border-l-4 border-amber-500">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-[var(--c-text)]">Database Migration Available</h3>
        <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-[10px] font-bold bg-amber-500 text-white animate-pulse">ACTION NEEDED</span>
      </div>
      <p class="text-[11px] text-[var(--c-text-dim)] leading-relaxed">
        We detected <strong id="legacyKeyCount" class="text-amber-500">0</strong> legacy keys in the <code class="text-[10px]">main</code> namespace. 
        Running this migration will move message counts, last-active timestamps, and invite data to dedicated namespaces for better performance and isolation.
      </p>

      <!-- Progress Bar (Hidden by default) -->
      <div id="migrationProgressWrap" class="hidden space-y-2 py-2">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">
          <span id="migrationPhaseLabel" class="text-amber-500">Starting...</span>
          <span id="migrationPercentLabel" class="text-[var(--c-text-muted)]">0%</span>
        </div>
        <div class="h-1.5 w-full bg-[var(--c-input)] rounded-full overflow-hidden border border-[var(--c-input-border)]">
          <div id="migrationProgressBar" class="h-full bg-amber-500 transition-all duration-300" style="width: 0%"></div>
        </div>
        <div id="migrationStatusLine" class="text-[10px] text-[var(--c-text-dim)] font-mono truncate">Preparing migration...</div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        <button type="button" id="stopMigrationBtn" onclick="stopDatabaseMigration()" class="hidden inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg text-xs font-bold bg-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-800 text-white transition-colors">
          <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" /></svg>
          Stop
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p id="maintenance-discord-cache" class="maint-group-label lg:col-span-2 scroll-mt-28">Discord &amp; Dashboard Cache</p>

    <div class="card p-5 space-y-3">
      <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-[var(--c-text)]">Discord Alignment</h3>
      <p class="text-[11px] text-[var(--c-text-dim)] leading-relaxed">Refetches <strong class="text-[var(--c-text-muted)]">channels and roles</strong> from Discord into the guild cache, then clears the same dashboard API caches as <strong class="text-[var(--c-text-muted)]">User Summary</strong>, <strong class="text-[var(--c-text-muted)]">Member Fetch</strong>, and <strong class="text-[var(--c-text-muted)]">Invites</strong> in the <strong class="text-[var(--c-text-muted)]">Dashboard Cache</strong> card on this page.</p>
      <button type="button" onclick="maintDiscordResync()" class="btn-dash-primary btn-dash-md">Resync Channels &amp; Roles</button>
      <p id="discordResyncHint" class="text-[10px] text-[var(--c-text-dim)] font-mono hidden"></p>
    </div>

    <div class="card p-5 space-y-4">
      <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-[var(--c-text)]">Dashboard Cache</h3>
      <p class="text-[11px] text-[var(--c-text-dim)] leading-relaxed">Clears in-memory caches for user summaries, member lists, and invites so the <strong class="text-[var(--c-text-muted)]">next</strong> dashboard load refetches from Discord and the database. Does <strong class="text-[var(--c-text-muted)]">not</strong> change anything on Discord itself.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        <button type="button" onclick="clearMaintCache(['user_summary'])" class="btn-dash-secondary btn-dash-sm">User Summary</button>
        <button type="button" onclick="clearMaintCache(['guild_members'])" class="btn-dash-secondary btn-dash-sm">Member Fetch</button>
        <button type="button" onclick="clearMaintCache(['invites'])" class="btn-dash-secondary btn-dash-sm">Invites List</button>
        <button type="button" onclick="clearMaintCache(['all'])" class="btn-dash-secondary btn-dash-sm">Clear All</button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p id="maintenance-backfill" class="maint-group-label lg:col-span-2 scroll-mt-28">Backfill &amp; Channel Jobs</p>

    <div class="card p-5 space-y-3 lg:col-span-2">
      <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-[var(--c-text)]">Seed Join History</h3>
      <p class="text-[11px] text-[var(--c-text-dim)] leading-relaxed">Backfills Recent Joins from members currently in the guild (newest Discord join times first). <strong class="text-[var(--c-text-muted)]">Invite codes</strong> cannot be reconstructed from this data; duplicate user+time pairs are skipped.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
        <label class="flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[10px] text-[var(--c-text-dim)]">
          <span class="whitespace-nowrap">Rows</span>
          <select id="maintInviteJoinSeedLimit" class="field-input text-xs py-1.5 min-h-0 w-[4.5rem]">
            <option value="25">25</option>
            <option value="50" selected>50</option>
            <option value="100">100</option>
            <option value="200">200</option>
          </select>
        </label>
        <button type="button" onclick="seedInviteJoinHistory()" class="btn-dash-primary btn-dash-sm">
          <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 16v1a3 3 0 003 3h10a3 3 0 003-3v-1m-4-8l-4-4m0 0L8 8m4-4v12"/></svg>
          Seed From Members
        </button>
      </div>
      <pre id="maintJoinHistorySeedPre" class="text-[10px] text-[var(--c-text-muted)] font-mono whitespace-pre-wrap break-words p-3 rounded-lg bg-[var(--c-input)] border border-[var(--c-input-border)]">Not run yet this session.</pre>
    </div>

    <div class="card p-5 space-y-4 lg:col-span-2">
      <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-[var(--c-text)]">Seed Last Message Times</h3>
      <p class="text-[11px] text-[var(--c-text-dim)] leading-relaxed"><strong class="text-[var(--c-text-muted)]">Channel scan</strong> walks message history in selected channels. <strong class="text-[var(--c-text-muted)]">Member search</strong> uses Discord’s Search Guild Messages API per human member (requires <code class="text-[10px]">MESSAGE_CONTENT</code>; may wait while the guild search index warms up; age-restricted channels are always included in search). Both upsert <code class="text-[10px]">last_message:&lt;userId&gt;</code> in Keyv. <strong class="text-[var(--c-text-muted)]">Only one</strong> backfill can run at a time.</p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
        <div>
          <label class="field-label text-[10px]">Strategy</label>
          <select id="maintSeedStrategy" class="field-input w-full text-sm min-h-[44px]" onchange="maintOnSeedStrategyChange()">
            <option value="channel_scan" selected>Channel history scan</option>
            <option value="member_search">Guild message search (per member)</option>
          </select>
        </div>
        <div>
          <label class="field-label text-[10px]">Delay Between Requests (ms)</label>
          <input type="number" id="maintDelayMs" class="field-input w-full text-sm min-h-[44px]" value="300" min="0" max="5000" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div id="maintSeedChannelOpts" class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
        <div>
          <label class="field-label text-[10px]">Max Messages Per Channel</label>
          <input type="number" id="maintMaxPerChannel" class="field-input w-full text-sm min-h-[44px]" value="10000" min="100" max="50000" />
        </div>
        <div>
          <label class="field-label text-[10px]">Max Members (search mode)</label>
          <input type="number" id="maintMaxMembers" class="field-input w-full text-sm min-h-[44px]" value="50000" min="1" max="50000" disabled title="Enable when using member search" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div id="maintSeedChannelScopeWrap">
        <label class="field-label text-[10px]">Channels</label>
        <label class="flex items-start gap-2.5 text-xs text-[var(--c-label)] cursor-pointer mb-2">
          <input type="checkbox" id="maintUseAllChannels" checked class="mt-0.5 rounded bg-[var(--c-input)] border-[var(--c-input-border)] text-[var(--c-accent)] focus:ring-[var(--c-accent)] shrink-0" onchange="maintOnAllChannelsChange()" />
          <span>All channels the bot can read (text, announcement &amp; thread channels)</span>
        </label>
        <div id="maintChannelListWrap" class="rounded-lg border border-[var(--c-input-border)] bg-[var(--c-input)]/30 overflow-hidden">
          <div id="maintChannelToolbar" class="flex flex-wrap justify-between items-center gap-2 px-2 py-1.5 border-b border-[var(--c-card-border)] bg-[var(--c-card)]/80">
            <span class="text-[9px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-[var(--c-text-dim)]">Or choose specific channels</span>
            <span class="flex gap-2">
              <button type="button" id="maintChSelectAllBtn" onclick="maintSelectAllChannelBoxes()" class="text-[10px] font-bold text-[var(--c-accent)] hover:underline disabled:text-[var(--c-text-dim)] disabled:pointer-events-none">Select All</button>
              <button type="button" id="maintChClearBtn" onclick="maintClearChannelBoxes()" class="text-[10px] font-bold text-[var(--c-text-dim)] hover:text-[var(--c-text)] hover:underline disabled:text-[var(--c-text-dim)] disabled:pointer-events-none">Clear</button>
            </span>
          </div>
          <div id="maintChannelList" class="max-h-52 overflow-y-auto p-2 space-y-1" data-loaded="0">
            <p class="text-[10px] text-[var(--c-text-dim)] px-1 py-2">Loading channels…</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-[11px] text-[var(--c-text-dim)] leading-relaxed mt-1.5">Uncheck <strong class="text-[var(--c-text-muted)]">All channels</strong> to limit the scan to the channels you tick below.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 items-center">
        <p class="text-[11px] text-[var(--c-text-dim)] leading-relaxed">Each user keeps the <strong class="text-[var(--c-text-muted)]">newest</strong> timestamp Keyv already had or that this run discovers.</p>
        <label class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-[var(--c-label)] cursor-pointer">
          <input type="checkbox" id="maintOnlyMissing" class="rounded bg-[var(--c-input)] border-[var(--c-input-border)] text-[var(--c-accent)]" />
          Only missing keys
        </label>
        <label class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-[var(--c-label)] cursor-pointer">
          <input type="checkbox" id="maintDryRun" class="rounded bg-[var(--c-input)] border-[var(--c-input-border)] text-[var(--c-accent)]" />
          Dry Run (No Writes)
        </label>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        <button type="button" id="maintStartSeedBtn" onclick="startMaintSeed()" class="btn-dash-primary btn-dash-md">Run Backfill</button>
        <button type="button" id="maintStopSeedBtn" onclick="stopMaintSeed()" class="hidden btn-dash-danger btn-dash-md">Stop</button>
      </div>

      <div id="maintSeedProgressWrap" class="hidden space-y-2 pt-2 border-t border-[var(--c-card-border)]">
        <div class="flex justify-between text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-[var(--c-text-dim)]">
          <span id="maintSeedPhaseLabel">Progress</span>
          <span id="maintSeedPercentLabel">0%</span>
        </div>
        <div class="h-2.5 rounded-full bg-[var(--c-input)] overflow-hidden border border-[var(--c-input-border)]">
          <div id="maintSeedProgressBar" class="h-full bg-[var(--c-accent)] transition-all duration-300 ease-out rounded-full" style="width:0%"></div>
        </div>
        <p id="maintSeedStatusLine" class="text-[11px] text-[var(--c-text-muted)] font-mono leading-relaxed"></p>
      </div>

      <div id="maintSeedSummary" class="hidden grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 text-center text-xs pt-2 border-t border-[var(--c-card-border)]">
        <div class="p-2 rounded-lg bg-[var(--c-input)] border border-[var(--c-input-border)]">
          <p class="text-[9px] uppercase font-bold text-[var(--c-text-dim)]">Messages Scanned</p>
          <p id="maintSumMessages" class="font-mono font-bold text-[var(--c-text)]">—</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-2 rounded-lg bg-[var(--c-input)] border border-[var(--c-input-border)]">
          <p class="text-[9px] uppercase font-bold text-[var(--c-text-dim)]">Users Tracked</p>
          <p id="maintSumTracked" class="font-mono font-bold text-[var(--c-text)]">—</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-2 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500/10 border border-emerald-500/25">
          <p class="text-[9px] uppercase font-bold text-emerald-400/90">Updated</p>
          <p id="maintSumUpdated" class="font-mono font-bold text-emerald-400">—</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-2 rounded-lg bg-[var(--c-input)] border border-[var(--c-input-border)]">
          <p class="text-[9px] uppercase font-bold text-[var(--c-text-dim)]">Skipped</p>
          <p id="maintSumSkipped" class="font-mono font-bold text-[var(--c-text-muted)]">—</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div id="maintSeedErrors" class="hidden text-[11px] text-red-400/90 font-mono whitespace-pre-wrap"></div>
    </div>

    <p id="maintenance-sessions" class="maint-group-label lg:col-span-2 scroll-mt-28">Sessions &amp; Keyv</p>

    <div class="card p-5 space-y-3">
      <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-[var(--c-text)]">Safe Cleanup</h3>
      <p class="text-[11px] text-[var(--c-text-dim)] leading-relaxed">Deletes dashboard session rows whose Keyv <strong class="text-[var(--c-text-muted)]">TTL is already in the past</strong>. <strong class="text-[var(--c-text-muted)]">Active</strong> sessions are left alone. Run <strong class="text-[var(--c-text-muted)]">Dry Run</strong> first to see counts before deleting.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        <button type="button" onclick="maintCleanupSessions(true)" class="btn-dash-secondary btn-dash-sm">Dry Run</button>
        <button type="button" onclick="maintCleanupSessions(false)" class="btn-dash-secondary btn-dash-sm">Delete Expired</button>
      </div>
      <pre id="cleanupSessionsPre" class="hidden text-[10px] text-[var(--c-text-muted)] font-mono whitespace-pre-wrap max-h-28 overflow-y-auto p-3 rounded-lg bg-[var(--c-input)] border border-[var(--c-input-border)] mt-2"></pre>
    </div>

    <div class="card p-5 space-y-3">
      <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-[var(--c-text)]">Session Hygiene</h3>
      <p class="text-[11px] text-[var(--c-text-dim)] leading-relaxed">Deletes <strong class="text-[var(--c-text-muted)]">every</strong> stored dashboard login session in Keyv. <strong class="text-[var(--c-text-muted)]">Everyone</strong> must sign in again—including this browser.</p>
      <button type="button" onclick="maintClearAllSessions()" class="btn-dash-danger btn-dash-md">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"/></svg>
        Log Out Everyone
      </button>
    </div>

    <p id="maintenance-backup" class="maint-group-label lg:col-span-2 scroll-mt-28">Backup &amp; Restore</p>

    <div class="card p-5 space-y-3 lg:col-span-2">
      <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-[var(--c-text)]">Database Backup</h3>
      <p class="text-[11px] text-[var(--c-text-dim)] leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">Downloads a <strong class="text-[var(--c-text-muted)]">JSON snapshot</strong> of the Keyv store—the same scope as <strong class="text-[var(--c-text-muted)]">Database Explorer</strong>. Treat the file as <strong class="text-[var(--c-text-muted)]">secret</strong>; it can contain session material and tokens.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        <button type="button" id="exportDbJsonBtn" onclick="exportDatabaseJson()" class="btn-dash-secondary btn-dash-md">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 shrink-0 opacity-90" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 16v1a3 3 0 003 3h10a3 3 0 003-3v-1m-4-4l-4 4m0 0l-4-4m4 4V4"/></svg>
          Export Database as JSON
        </button>
      </div>
      <div class="pt-2 border-t border-[var(--c-card-border)] space-y-2">
        <p class="text-[11px] text-[var(--c-text-dim)] leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">Imports a previously exported <code class="text-[10px]">nova-keyv-backup</code> JSON file. The server checks the payload before any write; use <strong class="text-[var(--c-text-muted)]">Validate</strong>, then <strong class="text-[var(--c-text-muted)]">Import</strong> to merge keys into Keyv.</p>
        <input type="file" id="importDbJsonInput" accept="application/json,.json" class="sr-only" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1" />
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row flex-wrap gap-2 items-stretch sm:items-center">
          <button type="button" id="importDbJsonPickBtn" onclick="document.getElementById('importDbJsonInput').click()" class="btn-dash-secondary btn-dash-md">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 shrink-0 opacity-90" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 7v10a2 2 0 002 2h14a2 2 0 002-2V9a2 2 0 00-2-2h-6l-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2z"/></svg>
            Choose Backup File…
          </button>
          <button type="button" id="validateDbJsonBtn" onclick="validateDatabaseJsonImport()" disabled class="btn-dash-secondary btn-dash-md disabled:pointer-events-none">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
            Validate
          </button>
          <button type="button" id="applyDbJsonBtn" onclick="applyDatabaseJsonImport()" disabled class="btn-dash-secondary btn-dash-md disabled:pointer-events-none">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 16.5v2.25A2.25 2.25 0 005.25 21h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0021 18.75V16.5M16.5 12L12 16.5m0 0L7.5 12m4.5 4.5V3"/></svg>
            Import
          </button>
        </div>
        <p id="importDbJsonFileLabel" class="text-[11px] text-[var(--c-text-dim)] font-mono hidden"></p>
        <pre id="importDbJsonStatus" class="hidden text-[11px] text-[var(--c-text-muted)] font-mono whitespace-pre-wrap break-words max-h-40 overflow-y-auto p-3 rounded-lg bg-[var(--c-input)] border border-[var(--c-input-border)]"></pre>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ MESSAGE CENTER -->
<section id="messaging" class="mb-10 page-section hidden">
  <div class="mb-6">
    <h2 class="section-heading mb-1">
      <svg class="w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 10h.01M12 10h.01M16 10h.01M9 16H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v8a2 2 0 01-2 2h-5l-5 5v-5z" /></svg>
      Message Center
    </h2>
    <p class="text-[11px] text-[var(--c-text-dim)] leading-relaxed">Send <strong class="text-[var(--c-text-muted)]">plain text</strong> or a <strong class="text-[var(--c-text-muted)]">rich embed</strong> as the bot to any channel you can select.</p>
  </div>
  <div id="messaging-composer" class="premium-card p-6 border-l-4 border-[var(--c-accent)] scroll-mt-28">
    <div class="mb-4">
      <h3 class="card-sub-title text-base font-semibold">Send as the bot</h3>
      <p class="card-sub-desc text-[11px] text-[var(--c-text-dim)] leading-relaxed mt-0.5">Uses your chosen channel; content is sent through the dashboard API (not stored as a draft).</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Controls -->
      <div class="space-y-5">
        <div>
          <label class="field-label">Target Channel</label>
          <select id="msg_channel_id" class="field-input channel-select"></select>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <label class="field-label">Message Mode</label>
          <div class="flex gap-2 p-1 bg-[var(--c-input)] rounded-lg border border-[var(--c-input-border)]">
            <button type="button" id="msg_mode_text" class="msg-mode-seg flex-1 min-h-[2.25rem] inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-md text-xs font-semibold transition-all whitespace-nowrap bg-[var(--c-accent)] text-white">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 6h16M4 12h10M4 18h14" /></svg>
              <span>Plain Text</span>
            </button>
            <button type="button" id="msg_mode_embed" class="msg-mode-seg flex-1 min-h-[2.25rem] inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-md text-xs font-semibold transition-all whitespace-nowrap text-[var(--c-text-dim)] hover:text-[var(--c-label)]">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" /></svg>
              <span>Rich Embed</span>
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div id="embed_color_wrap" class="hidden">
          <label class="field-label">Embed Color</label>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <input type="color" id="msg_embed_color" class="h-9 w-14" />
            <input type="text" id="msg_embed_color_text" class="field-input font-mono text-xs" placeholder="#999999" maxlength="7" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Editor -->
      <div class="sm:col-span-2 space-y-4">
        <!-- Plain Text Editor -->
        <div id="editor_text">
          <label class="field-label">Message Content</label>
          <textarea id="msg_content" rows="6" class="field-input font-sans leading-relaxed" placeholder="Type your message here... markdown is supported!"></textarea>
        </div>

        <!-- Rich Embed Editor -->
        <div id="editor_embed" class="hidden space-y-4">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div>
              <label class="field-label">Embed Title</label>
              <input type="text" id="msg_embed_title" class="field-input" placeholder="Title" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <label class="field-label">Thumbnail URL</label>
              <input type="url" id="msg_embed_thumbnail" class="field-input" placeholder="https://..." />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <label class="field-label">Embed Description</label>
            <textarea id="msg_embed_description" rows="4" class="field-input" placeholder="Description content..."></textarea>
          </div>
          <div>
            <label class="field-label">Footer Text</label>
            <input type="text" id="msg_embed_footer" class="field-input" placeholder="Footer text" />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex justify-end pt-2">
          <button id="sendMessageBtn" type="button" class="send-msg-btn px-8 inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M22 2L11 13M22 2l-7 20-4-9-9-4 20-7z" /></svg>
            <span data-btn-text>Send Message</span>
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

